_sText:
Hi,

this is my first map. It has been created with motives from cs_dustjump out of CS 1.6. I hope you like it.

Try to land in one of the three pools, one of the three cloth canopies (middle) or the well to survive the jump. Down in each of the houses is one teleporter to quickly return to the top.

This map is for max. 30 Players !


The Zip-file includes two versions:

de dustjump       - AWP and auto sniper are disabled.

de dustjump all   - All weapons can be used.


Otherwise both versions are exactly the same (v 1.2).


This map was created by: second ich
2010

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Unpack the Zip-file and move the file "de dustjump" or "de dustjump all" (or both) to:

Steam/SteamApps/"your name"/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

Have fun
